title: I can't see my club
body:
I'm a club master of Green River Korean Club
but only me, cannot access to my club
except my club is working well.
could you fix it for me.

replies.body:
We can work with you on fixing this if you reach out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) with the club name and tag. 

Let me know if you have any questions.
